        "locked": false,
        "body": "**Description:**\r\nWhen importing the OPML file from our project into feedly, most feeds are successfully imported. However, about 20 feeds fail with the following error:\r\n\r\n`Error--Failed to add feed/https://blog.algolia.com/blog/rss.xml`\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce:**\r\n\r\nExport the OPML file from the project.\r\nImport the OPML file into Feedly.\r\nObserve the error for specific feeds, including https://blog.algolia.com/blog/rss.xml.\r\n**Expected Behavior:**\r\nAll feeds in the OPML file should be imported successfully without any errors.\r\n\r\n**Actual Behavior:**\r\nA subset of feeds fails to import with the above error message.\r\n\r\n![스크린샷 2024-12-24 오후 8 47 30](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e77625bd-258f-43d4-a416-515c3800ca71)\r\n\r\n\r\nHere is the list of feeds that fail to import:\r\n<table><thead><tr><th>Feed Name</th><th>Category</th><th>Error URL</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Algolia</td><td>Engineering Blogs</td><td><a rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\" style=\"--streaming-animation-state: var(--batch-play-state-1); --animation-rate: var(--batch-play-rate-1);\" href=\"https://blog.algolia.com/blog/rss.xml\"><span style=\"--animation-count: 1; --streaming-animation-state: var(--batch-play-state-2);\">https</span><span style=\"--animation-count: 2; --streaming-animation-state: var(--batch-play-state-2);\">://blog</span><span style=\"--animation-count: 3; --streaming-animation-state: var(--batch-play-state-2);\">.algolia</span><span style=\"--animation-count: 4; --streaming-animation-state: var(--batch-play-state-2);\">.com</span><span style=\"--animation-count: 5; --streaming-animation-state: var(--batch-play-state-2);\">/blog</span><span style=\"--animation-count: 6; --streaming-animation-state: var(--batch-play-state-2);\">/rss</span><span style=\"--animation-count: 7; --streaming-animation-state: var(--batch-play-state-2);\">.xml</span></a></td></tr><tr><td>Codeship</td><td>Engineering Blogs</td><td><